Title: Boundaries, crosscaps and simple currents
Authors: J. Fuchs, L.R. Huiszoon, A.N. Schellekens, C. Schweigert, J. Walcher
Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX2e, reference added, typos corrected
Report-no: PAR-LPTHE 00-32, ETH-TH/00-9, CERN-TH/2000-220, NIKHEF-00-019
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B495 (2000) 427-434
\\
  Universal formulas for the boundary and crosscap coefficients are presented,
which are valid for all symmetric simple current modifications of the charge
conjugation invariant of any rational conformal field theory.
